             was indicted for <rs id="t17870912-8-off47" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17870912-8-off47" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17870912-8-off47" type="offenceSubcategory" value="animalTheft"></interp>
               feloniously stealing, on the <rs id="t17870912-8-cd48" type="crimeDate">31st of August</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17870912-8-off47 t17870912-8-cd48"></join>, two live pigs, value 40 s.
            </rs> the property of 
               
                  <persName id="t17870912-8-victim125" type="victimName">
                     James 
                     Aldridge
                  <interp inst="t17870912-8-victim125" type="surname" value="Aldridge"></interp>
